events.name: Washington State Cougars at Houston Cougars

headlines.description: Anthony Gordon threw for 440 yards and three touchdowns for his third straight 400-yard game as No. 20 Washington State pulled away in the second half to get a 31-24 win over Houston on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Gordon leads No. 20 Washington State over Houston 31-24

events.name: North Carolina Tar Heels at Wake Forest Demon Deacons

headlines.description: Jamie Newman came up with a pair of big plays on a clock-draining fourth-quarter drive, helping Wake Forest hold off North Carolina's comeback bid for a 24-18 win Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Wake Forest beats North Carolina 24-18 in nonconference game

events.name: Kansas Jayhawks at Boston College Eagles

headlines.description: Carter Stanley threw for three touchdowns, Khalil Herbert rushed for 187 yards on 11 carries, and Kansas stunned Boston College 48-24 on Friday night for its first road win over a Power 5 school in nearly 11 years.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jayhawks break 48-game road skid vs. Power 5
